                                                            </span>
                                                        </div>
                                                    </div>

                                                    <div class="card-body">
                                                        <div class="row">
                                                            <div class="col-md-6">
                                                                <div class="mb-3">
                                                                    <h5 class="text-primary">
                                                                        <i class="fas fa-wrench me-2"></i>Service Details
